---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Florida Medical Marijuana Evaluations | Releaf MD" 
  description="Book your medical marijuana evaluation in Florida today. Professional, private, physician-led assessments by Dr. Kelly Ennix King."
>
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        🩺 Service Landing Page
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark uppercase">Florida Medical Marijuana Evaluations</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Start your medical cannabis journey with a secure, compassionate clinical assessment.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">How the Initial Evaluation Works</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Florida Department of Health rules state that a patient must receive an in-person clinical assessment from a qualified certifying physician before obtaining an active card. This ensures that a professional doctor establishes a valid patient-physician relationship and directly monitors your care.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark">Evaluation Process Steps</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-3 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Step 1: Clinical Intake:</strong> Schedule your appointment and complete our online medical history questionnaire. Bring any relevant documents or prescription histories.</li>
          <li><strong>Step 2: Physician Consult:</strong> Meet privately with Dr. Kelly Ennix King. She reviews your symptoms, determines eligibility, and designs your initial routes and dosage recommendations.</li>
          <li><strong>Step 3: Registry Entry:</strong> Once approved, ReleafMD immediately enters your name and certification into the Florida Medical Marijuana Use Registry.</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Callouts / Cross-Linking -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Already Certified in Florida?</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              If you have an active card but need to renew your 30-week physician orders, check our <a href="/renewals" class="text-brand-accent font-bold hover:underline">Renewals Guide</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Qualifying Criteria</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Not sure if your medical diagnosis meets the state rules? <a href="/qualifying-conditions" class="text-brand-accent font-bold hover:underline">Check qualifying conditions here</a>.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">What's Included in Your Session</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Unlike high-volume "card mills", ReleafMD focuses on comprehensive clinical support. Your evaluation session automatically includes:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li>Full 70-day orders for all eligible administration methods.</li>
          <li>Registry profile setup assistance.</li>
          <li>A custom-crafted <a href="/treatment-plans" class="text-brand-accent font-bold hover:underline">Personalized Treatment Plan</a> showing specific cannabinoid ratios suitable for your symptoms.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            For more detail on regulations, read the <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=xnfeicu6jent0179" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Schedule Appointment
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
